quran[5{c,v,t}:
24,62,"momin to asal mein wohi hain jo Allah aur uss ke rasool ko dil se manen aur jab kisi ijtimai kaam ke mauqa par Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ke sath hon to uss se ijazat liye baghair nah jayen jo log tum se ijazat mangte hain wohi Allah aur rasool ke maan-ne walay hain, pas jab woh apne kisi kaam se ijazat mangeen to jisay tum chaho ijazat day diya karo aur aisay logon ke haq mein Allah se duaye mughfirat kya karo, Allah yaqeenan ghafoor o Raheem hai"
24,63,"musalmano, apne darmain Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ke bulanay ko aapas mein aik dosray ka sa bulana nah samajh betho Allah unn logon ko khoob jaanta hai jo tum mein aisay hain ke aik dosray ki aarr letay hue chupkay se stk jatay hain Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ke hukum ki khilaaf warzi karne walon ko darna chahiye ke woh kisi ftne mein girftar nah ho jayen ya un par dard naak azaab nah aa jaye"
24,64,"khabardaar raho, aasman o zameen mein jo kuch hai Allah ka hai tum jis rawish par bhi ho Allah uss ko jaanta hai jis roz log uss ki taraf پلٹیں ge woh unhen bta day ga ke woh kya kuch kar ke aeye hain woh har cheez ka ilm rakhta hai"
25,1,nihayat mutbarrik hai woh jis ne yeh Farqan apne bande par nazil kya taakay saaray Jahan walon ke liye Nazeer ho
25,2,"woh jo zameen aur asmano ki badshahi ka maalik hai, jis ne kisi ko beta nahi banaya hai, jis ke sath badshahi mein koi shareek nahi hai, jis ne har cheez ko peda kya phir is ki aik taqdeer muqarrar ki"
